WEBVTT

00:13:27.315 --> 00:13:31.451
Unaelewa unachopitia sio
sehemu ya mda,

00:13:31.475 --> 00:13:33.417
sio mfupa kua utajirudi,

00:13:33.441 --> 00:13:36.307
lakini kua umeguswa na kitu kikali.

00:13:36.919 --> 00:13:38.117
Kitu kisichotibika.

00:13:38.141 --> 00:13:40.997
Hakiui, lakini saa nyingine
yanakua kama yanaweza.

00:13:43.269 --> 00:13:46.848
Na kama hatuwezi kuzuia miongoni mwetu,

00:13:46.872 --> 00:13:48.189
nini tunaweza kufanya?

00:13:50.554 --> 00:13:54.874
Nini tunaweza kufanya zaidi ya
kukumbushiana

00:13:54.898 --> 00:13:57.604
kua vitu vingine havirekebishiki,

00:13:58.136 --> 00:14:01.318
na sio kila kidonda kinapaswa kupona.